Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:44.76,說明,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(839,624)\fad(0,400)}「夏日時光機.布魯斯2005」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:44.76,說明,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\pos(761,663)\fad(0,400)}攝影 原田直樹
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:46.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起學生時代留下的東西果然還是歐洲企劃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:49.83,說明,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(300,300)\pos(674,628)}2006年秋/第21次公演
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:49.83,說明,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(300,300)\pos(667,661)}Bluebirds·Breeders
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.99,0:17:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是周圍有朋友的話很受鼓舞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:54.50,說明,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(300,0)\pos(634,590)}2008年春夏
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:54.50,說明,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(300,0)\pos(702,624)}「如此溫柔的傀儡魔像」
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.53,0:17:54.50,說明,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\fad(300,0)\pos(648,661)}攝影 清水俊洋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.99,0:17:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天還有幾位客人要來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:57.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請進 歐洲企劃的成員
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:01.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.73,0:18:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.52,0:18:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能坐的下麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好窄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.52,0:18:12.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好熱鬧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.96,0:18:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走廊那裡堆的全是東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.85,0:18:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡車都開過來了 能不能行了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡車...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.18,0:18:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.89,0:18:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個很礙事的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.76,0:18:26.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,入口本來就這麼小了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.74,0:18:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諏訪 永野 角田
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.66,0:18:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3個人是一起的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下鴨幽水莊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.63,0:18:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是感覺被整了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.96,0:18:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 確實...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.88,0:18:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡車
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.12,0:18:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很想再要半疊的地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.88,0:18:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你這麼不高是不是為了遷就房子的高度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒那回事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,環境原因...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那裡要掛個暖爐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.09,0:18:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暖爐...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.52,0:19:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是暖爐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.02,0:19:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是馬甲麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.26,0:19:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒騙你們 穿給你們看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.14,0:19:09.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪像暖爐了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請教你們了哈 哪像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.75,0:19:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你趴下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.02,0:19:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看嘛 暖爐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 這個就作為給觀眾的禮物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.65,0:19:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在觀看DVD的各位中 將有一為幸運觀眾得到這件禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.85,0:19:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
